        Hi Robert,<br>
        <br>
        This is a known issue. The released binary was built on Windows
        Server 2008,  which has newer Windows system dependencies. We
        have fixed this problem and it is included for the next release.
        If you don't want to switch to another Windows version, I can
        build one working binary package and pass it to you off-list,
        meanwhile, you can also wait for the upcoming release.<br>
